data.text:
Indian actress Manisha Koirala and husband Samrat Dahal attend the opening of the seventh Indian Film Festival "Bollywood and Beyond" in Stuttgart, Germany, 21 July 2010. From 21 until 25 July 2010, about 50 feature films, short films and documentaries will be screened. Photo: Uwe Anspach
